  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK733">
<l>poṟaiyoruṅku mēlvaruṅkāṟ ṟāṅki yiṟaivaṟ</l>
<l>kiṟaiyoruṅku nērvatu nāṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A kingdom is that which can bear any burden that may be pressed on it (from adjoining kingdoms) and (yet) pay the full tribute to its sovereign.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
